Purpose of the Project

Traditional e-learning platforms often overwhelm learners with long courses and generic content. This project solves that problem by:

Breaking learning into short micro-lessons

Tracking learner activity and mastery levels

Generating personalized recommendations

Ensuring secure and scalable access through JWT authentication

